{"tid":1326340,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[歡迎入院] 連登精神病院再次啟用！","createTime":"2019-07-17T07:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T08:59:52.000Z","uid":60545,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"570723c71f40779de21e4882ce8b68387e3ab20e","tid":1326340,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eZRDT5X.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeZRDT5X.gif&h=e38c60a1&s={SIZE}\" />  <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>歡迎入院</strong></span></span> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eZRDT5X.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeZRDT5X.gif&h=e38c60a1&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n本院仲未<span style=\"font-size: small;\">壽</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">終</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">正</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">寢</span>㗎 今日又正式上線喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登本院山明水秀 環境青幽！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/27/Northville_Psychiatric_Hospital_Northville_Michigan.JPG/640px-Northville_Psychiatric_Hospital_Northville_Michigan.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F2%2F27%2FNorthville_Psychiatric_Hospital_Northville_Michigan.JPG%2F640px-Northville_Psychiatric_Hospital_Northville_Michigan.JPG&h=a3a6a54e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有一眾頂尖醫學人材照顧你地！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://easthillsvethospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/Welcome.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Feasthillsvethospital.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F08%2FWelcome.jpg&h=4fbfcded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://24.media.tumblr.com/b55a966746fb87d7c76f2a98b935e583/tumblr_mgb89ucG3Z1s23yneo1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F24.media.tumblr.com%2Fb55a966746fb87d7c76f2a98b935e583%2Ftumblr_mgb89ucG3Z1s23yneo1_500.gif&h=e35cab2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過記得喇！入咗院就冇得出院！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋提醒各位丸友同員工 呢排本院發現有保安同醫護人員冇<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">員工證</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我作為丸長喺度強調 任何員工均需於任何時間配戴員工證 <br />\n</span><br />\n否則視為非法入侵 手指難保(丸友飯餐有料加<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n好 我冇嘢講喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a5f456ab440b7b6b9976aedf3cdef613e05103","tid":1326340,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5786006810ba78d55ce50103db7c593ef99305c","tid":1326340,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:44:33.000Z","msg":"瘋"},{"pid":"ab9774f11b58fc07bd988c05bd24ebf799ac95c6","tid":1326340,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:47:28.000Z","msg":